## ğŸ”„ Template Synchronization

### Sync Process Requirements
- **Use sync scripts** for adding/updating templates from upstream
- **Never fork public repositories** directly to maintain privacy
- **Validate template functionality** after synchronization
- **Update documentation** to reflect any changes

### Sync Script Usage
```bash
# Add new template from upstream
./scripts/sync_template.sh template-name upstream-url stack-category

# Update existing template
./scripts/sync_template.sh existing-template upstream-url stack-category

# PowerShell version
.\scripts\sync_template.ps1 template-name upstream-url stack-category
```

### Upstream Attribution
- **Document original source** in `UPSTREAM.md`
- **Maintain license information** from upstream
- **Track last sync date** and version
- **Note any modifications** made to original template

